<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Murray, James Ramsey (1841-1905), MacFarland, John T. (1851-1913)</author>
<title>OLISDA, BESHIKSIZ OVULHONADA</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 OLISDA, BESHIKSIZ OVULHONADA
 GOʻDAK RABBIY ISO YOTAR OHURDA
 OSMONDAGI YORQIN YULDUZLAR BOQAR
 GOʻDAK RABBIY ISO SOMONDA UHLAR

[V2]
 ATROFIDA SHOVQIN BERAR CHORVALAR
 NAJOTKORIM ISO TINCHLIKDA YOTAR
 SEVAMAN SENI RAB - OSMON SOVGʻASI
 JANNAT SHOHANSHOHI, ABADIY SEVGI

[V3]
 BOR UMRIM SENGA MEN SAJDA QILAMAN
 NOMINGGA ABADIY SANO KUYLAYMAN
 RABBIM, NAJOTKORIM, SHOHIM VA DOʻSTIM
 ABADIYDIR SENING SHUHRATING, OMIN!</lyrics>
</song>